node.text:
In true #newyear fashion, I wanted to share my most loved video of 2020 🤍 This year was definitely like no other, and the most pivotal moments of this year are nowhere to be found on my feed.  While intangible, they were the most valuable — self growth, acceptance of situations out of my control, working under pressure but also putting time aside for self care.  Thank you for following along on my design journey — the messages, the love, and the support, shows me that there’s definitely hope in this world for a brighter future. There’s so much more to come in #2021 - let’s do this 🙌🏼
Credit: @decor.mm
